%% RHOAI Platform Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP TLS
    participant GatewayAPI as Gateway API<br/>HTTPRoute
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant vLLM as vLLM Runtime<br/>8000/TCP
    participant LLMD as llm-d EPP<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant RestProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP
    participant DSPAPI as DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST
    participant ArgoWF as Argo Workflows
    participant MLMeta as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant Guardrails as FMS Guardrails<br/>8033/TCP
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>8080/TCP
    participant TrainingOp as Training Operator
    participant GPU as GPU/CPU Worker

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: KServe Serverless Model Inference

    Client->>Route: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Route->>IstioGW: Forward<br/>TLS termination
    IstioGW->>vLLM: Route to InferenceService<br/>mTLS STRICT (Istio sidecar)
    vLLM->>GPU: Execute inference
    GPU-->>vLLM: Prediction result
    vLLM-->>IstioGW: JSON Response
    IstioGW-->>Route: Forward
    Route-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: KServe RawDeployment with Gateway API (llm-d)

    Client->>GatewayAPI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPRoute
    GatewayAPI->>LLMD: ext-proc gRPC/9002<br/>Routing decision request
    LLMD-->>GatewayAPI: Selected pod (KV-cache aware)
    GatewayAPI->>vLLM: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM->>GPU: Execute inference
    GPU-->>vLLM: Result
    vLLM-->>GatewayAPI: Streaming SSE Response
    GatewayAPI-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: ModelMesh Multi-Model Inference

    Client->>RestProxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>REST/8008
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: gRPC/8033 translation
    ModelMesh->>vLLM: Route to pod with model loaded<br/>via runtime-adapter/8085
    vLLM-->>ModelMesh: Inference result
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: gRPC response
    RestProxy-->>Client: REST response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 4: Pipeline Execution

    Client->>Dashboard: Submit pipeline<br/>HTTPS/8443 (OAuth)
    Dashboard->>DSPAPI: Create pipeline run<br/>REST/8888 Bearer Token
    DSPAPI->>MariaDB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306
    DSPAPI->>ArgoWF: Create Workflow<br/>Kubernetes API
    ArgoWF->>GPU: Execute pipeline steps
    ArgoWF->>MLMeta: Store artifact lineage<br/>gRPC/8080
    GPU-->>ArgoWF: Step complete
    ArgoWF-->>DSPAPI: Run complete
    DSPAPI-->>Dashboard: Status update

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 5: Guardrailed Inference

    Client->>Guardrails: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP/8033
    Guardrails->>Detectors: Input detection (PII, toxicity)<br/>HTTP/8080
    Detectors-->>Guardrails: Detection results
    Guardrails->>vLLM: Generate text<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>Guardrails: Generated text
    Guardrails->>Detectors: Output detection<br/>HTTP/8080
    Detectors-->>Guardrails: Safety results
    Guardrails-->>Client: Response with detection metadata

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 6: Distributed Training

    Client->>DSPAPI: Submit training pipeline<br/>REST/8888
    DSPAPI->>ArgoWF: Create training workflow
    ArgoWF->>TrainingOp: Create PyTorchJob<br/>Kubernetes API/6443
    TrainingOp->>GPU: Launch distributed training pods<br/>Multi-node GPU
    GPU-->>TrainingOp: Training complete
    TrainingOp-->>ArgoWF: Job status
    ArgoWF-->>DSPAPI: Pipeline complete
